MiniGameEventDetector - Class in com.worldbiomusic.minigameworld.minigameframes.helpers
Event detector to send Minigames

[IMPORTANT]
Detectable event means can get player from "Default event list" or "Detailed event list"

[Default Event List]
- PlayerEvent
- EntityEvent
- HangingEvent
- InventoryEvent
- InventoryMoveItemEvent
- PlayerLeashEntityEvent
- TabCompleteEvent

[Detailed Event list]
- Some of BlockEvent
- Some of EntityEvent
- Some of VehicleEvent
